{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "hyrelog-api-collection",
		"name": "HyreLog API",
		"description": "HyreLog API – Full collection.\n\n**V1 API:** Event ingestion, query, keys status, webhooks, exports (Bearer API key).\n**Dashboard:** Provisioning (companies, workspaces, keys), company-scoped reads, restore, admin (x-dashboard-token).\n\n**Setup:**\n1. Seed: `npm run seed` (optionally SEED_PLAN_TIER=STARTER/GROWTH)\n2. Set env: company_key, workspace_key, company_id, workspace_id, project_id, dashboard_token (from API .env DASHBOARD_SERVICE_TOKEN)\n3. For Dashboard flows set dashboard_company_id, dashboard_workspace_id, api_company_id (from Provision Company response).",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Root",
			"request": {
				"method": "GET",
				"header": [],
				"url": {
					"raw": "{{base_url}}/",
					"host": [
						"{{base_url}}"
					],
					"path": [
						""
					]
				},
				"description": "Root endpoint - no authentication required"
			},
			"response": []
		},
